762
00:57:36,079 --> 00:57:37,497
<i>You sure
you don't recognize him?</i>

763
00:57:39,415 --> 00:57:40,416
No.

764
00:57:40,500 --> 00:57:41,960
Fuck. What's wrong
with you, man?

765
00:57:42,043 --> 00:57:43,670
<i>Don't you wanna put
