775
00:58:15,743 --> 00:58:16,995
<i>Listen, I gotta be
honest with you.</i>

776
00:58:17,078 --> 00:58:18,871
<i>Right now
it's not looking good.</i>

777
00:58:18,955 --> 00:58:22,125
<i>Sometimes these cases
go months or even years
