778
00:58:22,792 --> 00:58:24,502
<i>You need to prepare
yourself for that.</i>

779
00:58:24,585 --> 00:58:25,586
(PANTING)

780
00:59:06,961 --> 00:59:08,713
<i>SUSAN: Why are you
