794
01:00:16,614 --> 01:00:18,116
We caught one
of the guys,

795
01:00:18,199 --> 01:00:20,326
one got killed
and one got away.

796
01:00:21,577 --> 01:00:22,912
What do you,
what do you want me to do?

797
01:00:24,372 --> 01:00:26,249
See if you recognize
the guy we caught.

798
01:00:27,792 --> 01:00:29,168
