forced their way into my car
with my wife and my daughter.

828
01:02:07,892 --> 01:02:10,728
And then this man...
This man? This man Lou?

829
01:02:10,811 --> 01:02:12,230
Yes. Lou, he made me
drive his car,

830
01:02:13,064 --> 01:02:15,107
he took me to the middle
of the desert
and he left me there.

831
01:02:15,191 --> 01:02:18,361
And later my wife
and daughter
were found dead

832
01:02:19,612 --> 01:02:20,738
near the same place.

833
01:02:25,451 --> 01:02:26,577
Well, that ain't right.

834
01:02:32,792 --> 01:02:33,793
(ANDES CLEARS THROAT)

835
01:02:36,379 --> 01:02:39,090
What you got to say
about this man's
wife and daughter?

836
01:02:39,173 --> 01:02:40,258
I don't know
nothing about that.

837
01:02:40,341 --> 01:02:41,676
I've never seen him
before in my life.

838
01:02:42,510 --> 01:02:44,387
What you gonna tell me
about Ray and Turk?

839
01:02:44,971 --> 01:02:46,514
Who?
Who?

840
01:02:48,307 --> 01:02:51,936
What, are you an owl?
You an owl, Lou?

841
01:02:52,812 --> 01:02:54,855
I never heard of 'em.
You never heard of 'em?

842
01:02:55,690 --> 01:02:56,691
No, sir.

843
01:03:01,487 --> 01:03:02,488
Hmm.

844
01:03:03,197 --> 01:03:04,198
Mmm-hmm.

845
01:03:05,366 --> 01:03:06,367
(CHUCKLES)

846
01:03:09,704 --> 01:03:10,746
All right.

847
01:03:14,500 --> 01:03:16,210
ANDES: Officer.
(DOOR OPENS)

848
01:03:16,335 --> 01:03:18,045
Put him up.
(DOOR CLOSES)

849
01:03:21,716 --> 01:03:24,468
Are you sure
this is the man?
Absolutely, yes.

850
01:03:24,885 --> 01:03:27,513
You'll swear in a court of law
