851
01:03:27,596 --> 01:03:28,597
Yes.

852
01:03:34,437 --> 01:03:35,521
Good.

853
01:03:37,440 --> 01:03:40,234
Well, we got Lou.

854
01:03:41,485 --> 01:03:42,945
I'm gonna charge him
with murder.

855
01:03:43,112 --> 01:03:44,572
What, do you have
enough evidence?

856
01:03:44,655 --> 01:03:47,658
Oh, you bet,
between you and the prints
in the car and the trailer.

857
01:03:47,742 --> 01:03:49,785
What, he went back
to the trailer
after he left me?

858
01:03:49,869 --> 01:03:53,205
Yeah, looks like it.
Uh, he probably just went back
to tell 'em where you were.

859
01:03:54,248 --> 01:03:55,708
That's why they came back
with the bodies.

860
01:03:55,916 --> 01:03:57,835
They were,
they were gonna kill you.

861
01:03:59,128 --> 01:04:00,379
You see? Yeah.

862
01:04:00,838 --> 01:04:03,674
I bet your friend Ray's
the third fella
in the hold-up.

863
01:04:04,842 --> 01:04:08,429
What HOW?
Well, you're gonna
wait for trial.

864
01:04:11,891 --> 01:04:13,434
And I'm gonna go find Ray.

865
01:04:20,733 --> 01:04:23,611
ALEX: Don't forget you have
a board meeting
at the museum at 3:00.

