01:04:25,446 --> 01:04:26,614
I'm sorry. What was that?

867
01:04:32,036 --> 01:04:33,371
You didn't sleep again,
did you?

868
01:04:37,291 --> 01:04:39,960
You know me.
I never sleep.

869
01:04:42,129 --> 01:04:44,757
My ex-husband
used to call me
a nocturnal animal.

870
01:04:44,840 --> 01:04:46,133
What ex-husband?

871
01:04:47,301 --> 01:04:49,512
I didn't know
you had an ex-husband.
Since when?

872
01:04:49,595 --> 01:04:51,639
A couple of years
in graduate school.

873
01:04:53,849 --> 01:04:55,851
It's weird,
I've been thinking
about him a lot lately,

874
01:04:55,935 --> 01:04:58,270
and then recently
he sent me this book
that he's written

875
01:04:58,354 --> 01:04:59,355
and it's

876
01:05:00,815 --> 01:05:02,149
