Nocturnal Animals
and he dedicated it to me.

878
01:05:07,488 --> 01:05:08,489
Did you love him?

879
01:05:08,572 --> 01:05:09,907
Yeah, I loved him.

880
01:05:11,492 --> 01:05:15,204
He was a writer and, uh,
I didn't have faith in him.

881
01:05:16,664 --> 01:05:18,707
I panicked
and I did something
horrible to him.

882
01:05:18,791 --> 01:05:20,960
Something unforgivable,
really.

883
01:05:22,044 --> 01:05:24,130
You left him?
I left him.

884
01:05:25,673 --> 01:05:28,217
I left him in a brutal way,

885
01:05:29,427 --> 01:05:31,887
