905
01:07:10,694 --> 01:07:12,738
No,no,ldo.
I just hate her, so...

906
01:07:12,821 --> 01:07:13,864
And I would like
to be more involved

907
01:07:13,948 --> 01:07:15,324
with Willow
throughout the day, so...

908
01:07:16,617 --> 01:07:18,452
Look. There she is.

909
01:07:19,370 --> 01:07:21,997
