01:07:39,139 --> 01:07:40,224
Well, you did see someone.

916
01:07:40,307 --> 01:07:41,976
That's Willow
and she's in her crib.

917
01:07:42,059 --> 01:07:43,269
She's sleeping.

918
01:07:43,686 --> 01:07:46,522
I'm really sorry
aboutyourphone.
I can, um...

919
01:07:47,314 --> 01:07:48,983
It's fine. A new one comes out
next week anyway, so...

920
01:07:49,066 --> 01:07:50,067
Thanks.

921
01:07:50,818 --> 01:07:52,152
(INHALES SHARPLY)
Shall we?

922
01:07:53,696 --> 01:07:54,697
They're all
waiting for us.

